title: Thank you payment for Jeff
body: This is a proposal to send Jeff a "thank you" payment using funds in the Unifund Treasury. Jeff has significantly improved the Unifund application and community. This thank-you payment is well deserved. This proposes a range for the payment as $200 - $1000. IGOV holders can vote on a value in that range and the weighted average will be used. For example, If 2 people vote for a $200 payment and 1 person votes for a $1000 payment, then Jeff will be sending $600 worth of IFUND. Please, vote and let's show Jeff our appreciation.
author: 0x65b0D5e1dc0dEE0704f53f660aA865C72e986fc7
